<h2>Sorry - you lost :(</h2>
<iframe src="//giphy.com/embed/3obiY2RsbUCnC" width="480" height="640" frameBorder="0" class="giphy-embed" allowFullScreen></iframe><p><a href="https://giphy.com/gifs/3obiY2RsbUCnC">via GIPHY</a></p>
<h3>You chose <%= @game.player.choice.capitalize %>. <%= @game.opponent.name %> chose <%= @game.opponent.choice.capitalize %>.</h3>
